## ğŸ’» CLI Interface

```bash
pv init
pv list
pv versions <prompt>
pv show <prompt> <version>
pv diff <prompt> <v1> <v2>
pv compare <prompt> <v1> <v2>
pv delete <prompt> <version>
pv rollback <prompt> <version>
pv dashboard --port 5000
```

